import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0):

    v1 = jnp.tanh(v0)
    v2 = jnp.maximum(v1, v0)
    v3 = jnp.tanh(v2)
    v4 = jnp.minimum(x0, v3)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(v0, v0)
